<div class="quotetitle">JohnJohn wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent"><br />How do I do this during gameplay?<br /></div><br />Open the game in FCEUXD. Hit the mushroom box and once the mushroom is out and moving pause the game. Open the hex editor (Tools -&gt; Hex Editor), scroll down until you see memory locations $0754 and $0756. Change $0754 to $00 (click the old value and type the new value) to make Mario big and $0756 to $01 to make him Super. Unpause the game and pick up the mushroom.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=95">tokumaru</a> — Fri Jan 22, 2010 3:18 pm</p><hr />
]]></content>
