<title type="html"><![CDATA[Super Mario and a super mushroom simultaneously on screen]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?t=5973&amp;p=55567#p55567"><![CDATA[
The game probably checks PlayerStatus when a box is hit to know whether a mushroom or a flower must show up. Then, both the mushroom and the flower probably just increment PlayerStatus when Mario picks them up. So yeah, picking up a mushroom while Super Mario will turn him into Fire Mario.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=95">tokumaru</a> — Fri Jan 22, 2010 3:09 pm</p><hr />
]]></content>
